GRAITEC is maker of CAD / CAE software for the civil engineering and construction industries.
Headquartered in France, the company was founded in 1986 by Francis Guillemard. GRAITEC went from a single company located in France to a group of 11 wholly owned companies spread around the world (France, Germany, Spain, Czech Republic, Italy, Slovakia, Russia, Romania, United Kingdom, Canada and USA). GRAITEC Group's turnover in 2015 was 68.7 million eurosâ‚¬ (+46% growth) with an EBITDA of 8% and the Group presently has more than 370 employees.
